    # game/areas/peltnorth2guards.rpy:486
    old "While {color=#f6d6bd}Dalit{/color} pats the boar, the guards get back to their own affairs. \n\n“Hero material, huh? Ain’t something I’m going to be jealous about, this trade of yours. I had a cousin who tried to get rich as a roadwarden. She kept it together for maybe half a year. Was lucky enough to die in a village, not in the middle of nowhere. At least she han’t woken up, the good folk burned her on a proper pyre.” "
