    # game/areas/peltnorth2guards.rpy:1528
    old "“Are you even going to find them? There should be none in these woods, the thicket is much too dense. And, you know, they’re cowards,” she simultaneously smiles and shrugs. “How much of a threat can they be? If you have to travel where they live, just be sure to have a few guards with you. They won’t attack a group of humans. Or take a crossbow. Or spells.” "
