    # game/areas/peltnorth2guards.rpy:1539
    old "“I han’t heard about someone studying them, you know? Those shouts,” she cups her hands around her mouth, “are like spells, and will make you sick. All it takes is what, a minute or so. Maybe a single one won’t be a threat, but they’re never alone. You’ll see packs of them in the north, and you better stay away from them, or be sure to have as many ways to keep them scared of you as you can. If they ain’t afraid, they ain’t going to let you live, and will devour you right after they deafen you.” "
